title: He's Into Her: Book 18
author: Maxinejiji
description: Part of the popular Filipino Wattpad-turned-published romance series  by Maxinejiji. This book continues the coming-of-age, school romance story involving friendship, love, drama and the lives of the series’ characters. Published as the 18th installment in the series’ second season. 256 pages. Published by Precious Pages Corporation / LIB Creatives.
